title: Everything 2020 Taught Me & My Hopes for 2021
description: 2020... we made it ya'll. In this episode, I will be speaking about the many things I learned within this life changing year. From personal to faith to career, I came to the realization of soooo many things. Some were eye opening in such good ways while others hurt for the better. I will also share what I hope to see and do in 2021. After a year like 2020, 2021 deserves to be the year of change.  Do not forget to follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanineamapola/ And Happy and Healthy Podcast on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/happyandhealthypodcast/ --- Send in a voice message: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/message Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/support
